---
import Tag from "../components/ui/Tag.astro"
export const partial = true;
---

<div class="w-full flex flex-wrap gap-8 justify-center">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 pb-10 border-b">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-between">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">nxtStore</h1>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <button class="p-2 border rounded-md bg-card text-card-foreground font-medium"
          ><a href="https://nxt-store.vercel.app/" target="_blank"
            >View Project</a
          >
        </button>
        <button class="p-2 border rounded-md bg-card text-card-foreground font-medium"
          ><a href="https://github.com/i-dkz/nxtStore" target="_blank"
            >View Git Repo</a
          ></button
        >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex gap-8 flex-wrap sm:flex-nowrap">
      <img
        src="/nxtstore.png"
        alt=""
        class="rounded-md w-[365px] sm:w-[50%] lg:w-[50%] shadow-lg"
      />
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <p class="">
          The aim of this project was to demonstrate my ability to create a
          nice, modern storefront, capable of requesting data from an API and
          displaying the data to the user.
        </p>
        <p>
          The user can add and delete items from the cart, and search for items.
        </p>
        <div class="w-full flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <Tag title="Next.js" />
          <Tag title="React.js" />
          <Tag title="Zustand" />
          <Tag title="Tailwind" />
          <Tag title="Axios" />
          <Tag title="Shadcn/UI" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-12">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-between">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Gameplus</h1>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <button class="p-2 border rounded-md bg-card text-card-foreground font-medium"
          ><a href="https://grand-monstera-b8f151.netlify.app/" target="_blank"
            >View Project</a
          >
        </button>
        <button class="p-2 border rounded-md bg-card text-card-foreground font-medium"
          ><a href="https://github.com/i-dkz/react-refresh" target="_blank"
            >View Git Repo</a
          ></button
        >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex gap-8 flex-wrap sm:flex-nowrap">
      <img
        src="/gameplus1.jpeg"
        alt=""
        class="rounded-md w-[365px] sm:w-[50%] lg:w-[50%] shadow-lg"
      />
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <p class="">
          This is a game directory app that shows up to date games from the
          RAWG.io API. The user has search functionality, and filtering to find
          the most up to date games.
        </p>

        <div class="w-full flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <Tag title="React.js" />
          <Tag title="ChakraUI" />
          <Tag title="Axios" />
          <Tag title="Vite" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
